**Prompt to Create Aesthetic Dropdown with Beautiful Panel and Typography**

Create an elegant, aesthetic dropdown that opens as a beautiful panel with refined typography and visual design (no emojis). Focus on clean, sophisticated UI with excellent spacing, typography, and subtle animations.

**Aesthetic Dropdown Design Requirements:**

**1. Sophisticated Trigger Button:**
```css
.dropdown-elegant {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 320px;
  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
}

.dropdown-trigger-elegant {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  background: #ffffff;
  border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: #2d3748;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  transition: all 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  font-weight: 450;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
}

.dropdown-trigger-elegant:hover {
  border-color: #c3dafe;
  background: #f8fafc;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);
}

.dropdown-trigger-elegant:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: #6366f1;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
}

.trigger-icon {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  color: #64748b;
  font-size: 12px;
  margin-left: 8px;
}
```

**2. Beautiful Dropdown Panel:**
```css
.dropdown-panel {
  position: absolute;
  top: calc(100% + 8px);
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  background: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 14px;
  box-shadow: 
    0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
  overflow: hidden;
  z-index: 1000;
  animation: panelSlideDown 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
}

@keyframes panelSlideDown {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(-12px) scale(0.98);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
  }
}

.panel-header {
  padding: 16px 20px 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
  color: #475569;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.panel-content {
  max-height: 280px;
  overflow-y: auto;
  padding: 4px 0;
}
```

**3. Elegant List Items:**
```css
.dropdown-option {
  padding: 13px 20px;
  color: #334155;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.015em;
  line-height: 1.5;
  position: relative;
}

.dropdown-option:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
  color: #1e293b;
  padding-left: 24px;
}

.dropdown-option.selected {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
  color: #1d4ed8;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.option-indicator {
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.dropdown-option.selected .option-indicator {
  background: #3b82f6;
  border-color: #3b82f6;
}

.option-checkmark {
  color: white;
  font-size: 10px;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: scale(0.5);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.dropdown-option.selected .option-checkmark {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: scale(1);
}

.option-label {
  flex: 1;
  margin-left: 14px;
}
```

**4. Implementation with Beautiful Typography:**
```javascript
const ElegantDropdown = () => {
  const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false);
  const [selected, setSelected] = useState('prefer-not');

  const options = [
    { id: 'male', label: 'Male', description: 'Identify as male' },
    { id: 'female', label: 'Female', description: 'Identify as female' },
    { id: 'nonbinary', label: 'Non-binary', description: 'Identify outside the binary' },
    { id: 'prefer-not', label: 'Prefer not to say', description: 'Keep this private' }
  ];

  return (
    <div className="dropdown-elegant">
      <button 
        className="dropdown-trigger-elegant"
        onClick={() => setIsOpen(!isOpen)}
      >
        <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'flex-start' }}>
          <span style={{ fontSize: '13px', color: '#64748b', marginBottom: '2px' }}>
            Gender Preference
          </span>
          <span style={{ fontSize: '15px', fontWeight: '500', color: '#1e293b' }}>
            {options.find(opt => opt.id === selected)?.label}
          </span>
        </div>
        <span 
          className="trigger-icon"
          style={{ transform: isOpen ? 'rotate(180deg)' : 'rotate(0deg)' }}
        >
          ▼
        </span>
      </button>

      {isOpen && (
        <div className="dropdown-panel">
          <div className="panel-header">
            Select Gender
          </div>
          <div className="panel-content">
            {options.map((option) => (
              <div
                key={option.id}
                className={`dropdown-option ${selected === option.id ? 'selected' : ''}`}
                onClick={() => {
                  setSelected(option.id);
                  setIsOpen(false);
                }}
              >
                <div className="option-indicator">
                  <span className="option-checkmark">✓</span>
                </div>
                <div className="option-label">
                  <div style={{ fontSize: '15px', fontWeight: '500' }}>
                    {option.label}
                  </div>
                  <div style={{ 
                    fontSize: '12px', 
                    color: selected === option.id ? '#60a5fa' : '#94a3b8',
                    marginTop: '2px'
                  }}>
                    {option.description}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
};
```

**5. Visual Result:**

**Closed State:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Gender Preference                       │
│ Prefer not to say                   ▼   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Opened State:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Gender Preference                       │
│ Prefer not to say                   ▼   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
          ↓
          ┌─────────────────────────────┐
          │       Select Gender         │
          │  ○ Male                    │
          │    Identify as male        │
          │                            │
          │  ○ Female                  │
          │    Identify as female      │
          │                            │
          │  ○ Non-binary              │
          │    Identify outside binary │
          │                            │
          │  ● Prefer not to say       │
          │    Keep this private       │
          └─────────────────────────────┘
```

**6. Design Features:**
- Subtle gradients and shadows
- Perfectly rounded corners
- Elegant typography hierarchy
- Smooth animations with cubic-bezier
- Blurred backdrop for modern look
- Two-line options with descriptions
- Custom radio indicators
- Hover effects with gradient backgrounds
- Clean spacing and alignment

**7. Color Palette:**
- Background: `#ffffff` / `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98)`
- Text primary: `#1e293b`
- Text secondary: `#64748b`
- Border: `#e2e8f0` → `#c3dafe` (hover)
- Accent: `#3b82f6` (blue)
- Shadow: subtle multi-layer shadows

**Result:** A truly aesthetic dropdown panel that looks like it's from a premium design system, with perfect typography, spacing, animations, and visual polish.

